        <p class="text-red-700 font-medium">✗ Salary below median wage threshold (NZ$65,700). Retail manager not on exemption list. Employer tried Job Check but rejected. Would need higher salary or different role. Advised to look at roles meeting median wage or on shortage list.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

